pageContext.claim: “We'll let Obamacare fail and then the Democrats are going to come to us and they're going to say 'how do we fix it, how do we fix it,' or 'how do we come up with a new plan.'”
pageContext.analysis: Trump has not reached out to Democrats, but pursued a Republican-only strategy. Democrats have said they are willing to negotiate if full repeal of Obamacare is taken off the table.
